{
  "texts": [
    "Second, focusing on news limits system performance on more diverse data (e.g.",
    "conversation, vlogs, etc.).",
    "To investigate the role of SEE in tasks such as summarization, previous entity-centric work (Fan et al., 2018; He et al., 2022; Xiao and Carenini, 2022) has compared summaries generated by entity-aware methods with generic summarization methods qualitatively.",
    "As part of our evaluation, we combine manual and automatic, qualitative and quantitative analyses to assess SEE impact on several approaches to summarization.",
    "In this paper, we therefore present and evaluate a gold standard dataset manually annotated with SEE labels, by identifying all entities that appear in a human-written summary as salient, making the task less subjective."
  ]
}